# Pairs with branch protection's "Require review from Code Owners".
# A PR that touches any of the paths below cannot merge until the named
# reviewer approves — robotic checks alone aren't sufficient for these
# security-critical surfaces.
#
# Lines later in the file override earlier ones, so the catch-all goes
# first and specific high-risk paths follow.

# Catch-all — every PR routes a code-owner request, but in practice
# self-approval is sufficient for ordinary changes.
